## Parsed with column specification:
## cols(
##   query_id = col_character(),

##   evalue = col_double(),
##   bit_score = col_double(),

##   subject_group = col_character()

rumino %>%
  count(query_id)
## # A tibble: 1 x 2
##   query_id                      n
##   <chr>                     <int>
## 1 Ruminococcus_gnavus_query    10
rumino %>%
  count(subject_id, subject_species)
## # A tibble: 10 x 3
##    subject_id subject_species                  n
##    <chr>      <chr>                        <int>
##  1 AJ515913   Ruminococcus champanellensis     1
##  2 EF529620   Ruminococcus gauvreauii          1
##  3 FJ611794   Ruminococcus faecis              1
##  4 L76596     Ruminococcus callidus            1
##  5 L76598     Ruminococcus albus               1
##  6 L76600     Ruminococcus bromii              1
##  7 L76602     Ruminococcus lactaris            1
##  8 L76603     Ruminococcus flavefaciens        1
##  9 L76604     Ruminococcus torques             1
## 10 X94967     Ruminococcus gnavus              1
rumino %>%
  group_by(subject_group) %>%
  summarize(mean_pct_identity = mean(pct_identity))
## # A tibble: 2 x 2
##   subject_group mean_pct_identity
##   <chr>                     <dbl>
## 1 Group I                    83.9
## 2 Group II                   95.1
rumino %>%
  ggplot() +
  geom_boxplot(aes(y=pct_identity, x=subject_group))

rumino %>%
  ggplot() +
  geom_boxplot(aes(y=pct_identity, x=subject_group)) +
  labs(x="Species group", y="Percent identity to R. gnavus")

rumino %>%
  ggplot() +
  geom_boxplot(aes(y=pct_identity, x=subject_group)) +
  labs(x="Species group", y="Percent identity to R. gnavus") +
  theme_bw()

rumino %>%
  ggplot() +
  geom_point(aes(y=pct_identity, x=bit_score))

rumino %>%
  ggplot() +
  geom_point(aes(y=pct_identity, x=bit_score, color=subject_group))

rumino %>%
  ggplot() +
  geom_point(aes(y=pct_identity, x=bit_score, color=subject_group)) +
  scale_color_brewer(palette = "Set1") +
  labs(y="Percent identity", x="BLAST bit score", color="Species group") +
  theme_bw()
